                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.002/29</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Russell</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams—Extracts]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-01-03T08:00:00-04:40">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 3, 1916, 8 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Resignation of Minister of Finance has been accepted and son of the President,
                    the Minister of Interior, has been appointed in his place. Peynado, Minister of
                    Justice, has been appointed to the Ministry of Interior.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Russell</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
